description:
make sure you care for the people you love, and the people who care for you


Press Z/X to cycle through colors (or tap the little buttons under the screen).

Tap/Click the screen to get a new generated configuration. 

Save a gif by pressing ctrl+9. `Right click -> save as` to save the gif. You may need to have this NFT in its own window for the gif recording to work.
